---
title: Carb Smart Beyond Meat® and Mushroom Soup with Crispy Shallots and Garlic Toasties
description: You won't miss the potatoes in this Beyond Meat® and mushroom soup! This meal is filled to the brim with veggies and topped with crispy shallots for a hit of saltiness!

